name: Subterror Nemesis Sorcerer
effect:
FLIP: You can target 1 "Subterror" card in your GY; add it to your hand.
You can target 1 face-down "Subterror" monster you control; Special Summon this card (from your hand), and if you do, change that target to face-up Attack or Defense Position. You can target 1 face-up "Subterror" monster on the field; change it to face-down Defense Position, and if you do, Special Summon 1 "Subterror" monster from your Deck in face-up or face-down Defense Position, except "Subterror Nemesis Sorcerer". You can only use each effect of "Subterror Nemesis Sorcerer" once per turn.
